At Studify.Services, we take the privacy of our users seriously. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our website.

Collection of Personal Information
We collect personal information such as name, gender, subjects you are studying, email address, profile picture, and location data when you register on our website. We collect this information to provide better services such as notes, previous year question paper, and other academic resources to students of IIT Madras.

Use of Personal Information
We use your personal information to provide you with the academic resources you need to excel in your studies. We may use your personal information to contact you about important exam dates or to notify you about updates to our website. We do not share your personal information with any third-party vendors or organizations.

Protection of Personal Information
We take the protection of your personal information seriously. We use industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. We restrict access to your personal information to only those individuals who need access to provide services to you.

Accessing and Updating Personal Information
You can access and update your personal information at any time by logging into your account on our website. You can also contact us directly if you need assistance accessing or updating your personal information.

Children's Privacy
Our website is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13. If you are under the age of 13, please do not use our website.

Changes to this Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes to this policy will be posted on our website. By continuing to use our website after any changes to this policy, you are agreeing to the updated policy.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at privacy@studify.services.

Last updated: February 24, 2023.
